Key Match Events: Bucks lost 105-102 to the Trail Blazers on Saturday
Post-Match Reflections: Giannis Antetokounmpo is taking the losses on his shoulders and is trying everything he can to be better
Miscellaneous Highlights: Giannis Antetokounmpo offered a strange analogy about his play, comparing it to a savings account
Others: The Bucks are in a tie with the Heat for fifth in the East and are just one game ahead of the ninth spot, which is currently held by the Pistons
